OL,3,CThe loneliness of the long distance
OL,4,Ccyclist
OL,6,FOnly one out of more than two thousand
OL,7,Friders is set to fully complete the
OL,8,FLondon Edinburgh London ultra-cycling
OL,9,Fevent after Storm Floris caused the
OL,10,Forganisers to halt the race.
OL,12,FThe 1400km event takes place once
OL,13,Fevery four years and more than 2500
OL,14,Friders from 57 countries began the
OL,15,Fchallenge on Saturday.
OL,17,FDue to the exceptionally high winds in
OL,18,FScotland and on high ground on Monday,
OL,19,Forganisers decided that it would be
OL,20,Funsafe for riders to continue north
OL,21,Fpast Cumbria.
