OL,3,CThe loneliness of the long distance
OL,4,Ccyclist
OL,6,FITV Border reporter Ryan Dollard
OL,7,Fcaught up with Ian as he reached the
OL,8,Fcheckpoint at Brampton in Cumbria.
OL,10,FIan said: "The conditions were some of
OL,11,Fthe worst I've ever ridden. The bike
OL,12,Fran all over the place, and I'm lucky
OL,13,Fthe roads were empty.
OL,15,F"I'm always determined to complete
OL,16,Fwhat I start, and I'm heading back to
OL,17,FLondon now. I'm going to ride all
OL,18,Fnight."
